{"tid":2176430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】消息指新增 20 人確診　屯門醫院 81 歲女病人離世　累計 80 死","createTime":"2020-08-27T05:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T05:41:14.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0f8a8845cd68ecf39105cd10daa6d1c87ad70a19","tid":2176430,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"屯門醫院發言人公布，一名確診武漢肺炎的 81歲女病人（個案編號：3960）於今日離世。另外消息指今天確診宗數 20 宗，詳情稍後會在衞生署記者會公佈。<br />\n<br />\n離世病人有長期病患，在本月七日因發燒及咳嗽入住屯門醫院接受治療。其後情況持續惡化，延至今日上午 11 :55 離世。院方指對病人離世感到難過，會為家屬提供適切協助。<br />\n<br />\n連同這位離世的女長者，至今共有 80 名武漢肺炎確診病人離世。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E-20-%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2-81-%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%96-%E7%B4%AF%E8%A8%88-80-%E6%AD%BB/?fbclid=IwAR37zHr9Szq3JxPjQFDIqqpE0rk6K5nC_yA2rWqvBAxSG6EqgB9GbbTfOiE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A2%259E-20-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2-81-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25B8%2596-%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E8%25A8%2588-80-%25E6%25AD%25BB%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR37zHr9Szq3JxPjQFDIqqpE0rk6K5nC_yA2rWqvBAxSG6EqgB9GbbTfOiE&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk3XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=f33da925\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A2%259E-20-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2-81-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%